Durban - A pilot has died following a helicopter crash in Eshowe on Thursday afternoon. According to Paul Herbst from IPSS Medical Rescue when paramedics arrived the pilot of the light aircraft sustained fatal injuries and was declared dead on the scene. Herbst said the light aircraft was still up in flames. To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
